- Aye, aye.

32:21.520 --> 32:22.794
- Real Old Tom.
- Aye.

32:22.880 --> 32:25.838
- Dead Tom?
- Aye, aye.

32:27.000 --> 32:29.992
Cool.

32:30.080 --> 32:31.991
- Clueless Morgan?
- Huh?

32:32.080 --> 32:34.071
